  30:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac_ex.c ****       (+) When Dual mode is enabled (i.e. DAC Channel1 and Channel2 are used simultaneously) :
  31:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac_ex.c ****           Use HAL_DACEx_DualGetValue() to get digital data to be converted and use
  32:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac_ex.c ****           HAL_DACEx_DualSetValue() to set digital value to converted simultaneously in
  33:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_dac_ex.c ****           Channel 1 and Channel 2.
